reviewText:
Unfortunately their is no Tempest Storm in this collection.  She has one three minute PG rated scene with Bettie Page and the rest are old grainy black and whites of various girls.  Not Tempest.  I expected and understand the grainy, but I know Tempest has more than one scene.

Very Very Disappointed

If you're a serious Tempest Storm fan and expect to see her throughout this dvd...DON"T BUY THIS!!  A major disappointment and a very deceptive title to this disc considering that Tempest is only on during the first 2 or 3 minutes of it followed by unknowns on grainy film.  Don't waste your time or money!!

VERY POOR quality, only two Tempest Storm clips, one so bad hard to tell who it was. has several older dancers lousy quality though.
save your money and time.
